# Business Rules

## Tone
- Professional operator tone; no hype.
- Separate facts, hypotheses, and decisions.

## Structure
- Strategy notes link to [[Goals and OKRs]] and [[ROADMAP]].
- Product notes include stage, audience, and validation status.
- Revenue notes distinguish model vs active offer.

## Non-Goals
- Do not store banking credentials, tax IDs, or private financial account numbers.
- Keep sensitive personal finance detail out of Git if not needed for ops.
